headline: ‘Human Grave,’ With No Body, Is Revealed in Dulos Case
abstract: Her body has not been discovered. But the suspect was linked to the six-foot-long hole at the Connecticut club, the arrest warrant says.
lead_paragraph: STAMFORD, Conn. — Nearly eight months after Jennifer Dulos, a mother of five from an affluent Connecticut suburb, was reported missing, the authorities revealed a chilling new detail in the case.
